attle with police. Kretschmer committed suicide during the exchange of gunfire.<ref name=\"guardian12-03\">{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2009/mar/12/school-shooting-germany-letter|title=Teenage killer wrote letter to parents saying he 'couldn't go on'|last=Davies|first=Lizzy|date=2009-03-12|work=[[The Guardian]]|accessdate=2009-03-12|location=London}}</ref><ref name=\"BBCmain\">{{cite news\n|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/7936817.stm |title='German school gunman 'kills 15' |accessdate=2009-03-11 |work=BBC News |date=2009-03-11}}</ref><ref name=\"Stuttgart Journal\">{{cite web |url=http://www.stuttgart-journal.de/tp/pool/nachrichten-stuttgart/sj/2009/03/12/news/amoklauf-von-winnenden-polizei-konstruiert-genauen-tathergang/|title=Polizei konstruiert genauen Tathergang (Police reconstruct exact events)|accessdate=2009-03-13|publisher=Stuttgart Journal|date=2009-03-13|language=German}}</ref>\n|-\n| March 30, 2009\n| [[Pietermaritzburg]],<br>[[KwaZulu-Natal]],<br>South Africa\n| ..., 17;<br>..., 19\n| 1 dead\n|\n| 17-year-old student Nhlanhla Buthelezi died from stab wounds to the chest and back outside a classroom of Amakholwa High School, near [[Pietermaritzburg]], South Africa. The two assailants, a 17-year-old student and his 19-year-old cousin, fled the school.<ref name=\"thestar331\">{{cite news|title=Boy dies after school stabbing|date=2009-03-31|url =http://www.thestar.co.za/?fArticleId=4913906|work=[[The Star (South Africa)]]|accessdate = 2009-05-28}}</ref>\n|-\n| April 29, 2009\n| [[Portmore, Jamaica|Portmore]],<br>[[Saint Catherine Parish|St. Catherine]],<br>[[Jamaica]]\n| ..., 15\n|\n| 1 injured\n| The [[Dean (academics)|Dean of Discipline]] of [[Ascot High School]], in [[Portmore, Jamaica|Portmore]], [[Jamaica]], was stabbed in the neck while inside his office by a 15-year-old student at the school. The dean was treated at a local hospital and released.<ref name=\"jamaicastardean\">{{cite news|title=Dean of discipline stabbed|date=