es.com |date=2009-11-01 |accessdate=2011-03-12}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Decker |first=Cathleen |url=https://www.latimes.com/news/local/la-me-week8-2009nov08,0,7914780.story |title=Melody Ross touches the world |publisher=Latimes.com |date=2009-11-08 |accessdate=2011-03-12}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/homicidereport/2009/11/times-coverage-funeral-held-for-melody-ross-16.html |title=Funeral held for Melody Ross, 16 |work=LA Times |date=2009-11-15 |accessdate=2011-03-12}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.presstelegram.com/news/ci_13729826 |title=Teens charged as adults in Melody Ross case |publisher=Presstelegram.com |date=2010-03-09 |accessdate=2011-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110613212140/http://www.presstelegram.com/news/ci_13729826 |archive-date=2011-06-13 |url-status=dead }}</ref> Vinson was sentenced to 155 years of prison. Davis was sentenced to 8 years on a manslaughter charge.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/lanow/2011/12/bellflower-teen-sentenced-to-155-years-in-wilson-high-students-death.html |title=Gang member gets 155 years in slaying of honors student Melody Ross |newspaper=[[Los Angeles Times]] |date=December 19, 2011 |accessdate=September 1, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n===2010s===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"font-size:90%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:65px;\"| Date\n! style=\"width:85px;\"| Location\n! style=\"width:75px;\"| Attacker(s)\n! data-sort-type=\"number\" style=\"width:75px;\"| Dead{{r|group=lower-alpha|note_a}}\n! data-sort-type=\"number\" style=\"width:75px;\"| Injured{{r|group=lower-alpha|note_a}}\n! Description\n|-\n| February 5, 2010\n| [[Madison, Alabama|Madison]],<br>[[Alabama]],<br>[[United States]]\n| Hammad Memon, 14\n| 1 dead\n|\n| Todd Brown, a 14-year-old ninth-grade student, was shot in the back of the head in a hallway of Discovery Middle School in [[Madison, Alabama]] by another student, Hammad Memon. Brown was transported to a hospital in [[Hunt